Aurora.KQDK-CD: KQDK-CD, virtual and UHF digital channel 39, is a low-power Class A television station serving Denver, Colorado, United States that is licensed to Aurora. It is a translator of Cheyenne, Wyoming-licensed CTN owned-and-operated station KQCK (channel 39) that is owned by the Christian Television Network. KQDK's transmitter is located on East Iliff Avenue (near Colorado Highway 83) in southeastern Denver.
